---
title: Crispy Shrimp and Green Beans with Coconut Rice and Plum Sauce
description: This Thai-inspired dish is faster than takeout but hits all the right taste notes! You'll love the creamy coconut rice  paired with the crunch of crispy shallots. A sweet and savoury sauce brings it all together.
